Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.52,0:00:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.94,0:00:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.28,0:00:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I can dodge it if I watch closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.99,0:00:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't get hit, \Nit doesn't matter what weapon he uses.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.30,0:00:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.72,0:00:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.22,0:00:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.39,0:00:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That kid's pretty good!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.47,0:01:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He was able to hit the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.72,0:01:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick guys like him are tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.98,0:01:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This could turn out to be a good fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.65,0:01:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! I can't cut him. \NHe's wearing chain mail underneath.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.57,0:01:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad, I liked these.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.94,0:01:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you're not afraid of my ax?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.70,0:01:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a lot of guts. You're just like Thors.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.41,0:01:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You big bastard. Who are you to my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.96,0:01:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't tell you? That's so cold of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.67,0:01:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard he's descended from a jarl. \NHe was of noble origin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.89,0:01:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Helga's the one from a family of jarls.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.02,0:01:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thors rose through the ranks \Nbecause of his skill with the sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.94,0:01:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.19,0:01:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to know more?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.77,0:01:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.28,0:01:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want me to tell you,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.36,0:01:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll have to entertain me some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.95,0:02:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, Thorfinn?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.95,0:02:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I can entertain you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.25,0:02:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's going to be hard holding back enough \Nto make sure you can still talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.34,0:02:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what you're saying, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.47,0:02:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,My stomach hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.84,0:02:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Holding back on the captain? You?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.51,0:02:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Go easy on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.51,0:02:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an idiot! You're an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.31,0:02:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.27,0:02:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I consider Thorfinn to be a warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.36,0:02:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.57,0:02:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thors was stronger than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.99,0:02:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Prove to me that you really are Thors' child,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.04,0:02:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thorfinn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.93,0:04:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That stupid kid. He came back here to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.10,0:04:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to the prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.23,0:04:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Over there! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.28,0:04:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold down his leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.24,0:04:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,OUT OF THE CRADLE
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.49,0:04:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Do the same over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.66,0:04:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I can hear the sound the of battle nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.33,0:04:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.71,0:04:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have anything better to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.63,0:05:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.26,0:05:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to open my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.01,0:05:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to stay asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.89,0:05:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,like this... forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.02,0:05:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Highness... Your Highness... \NYour Highness Canute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.83,0:05:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ragnar! You're still alive--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.46,0:05:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a dream, isn't it, Ragnar?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.14,0:05:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I came to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.14,0:06:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going? You'll leave me behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.61,0:06:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you telling me to live alone in a world like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.78,0:06:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I can survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.50,0:06:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.96,0:06:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,failed as the person tasked \Nwith your education.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.63,0:06:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I was supposed to raise you as a jarl. \NBut I raised you as a normal child,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.97,0:06:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,like a farmer would raise his own child.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.52,0:06:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I knew that's not what the king wanted. \NPlease forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.61,0:06:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with that? You understood my feelings \Nbetter than my father, the king!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.83,0:07:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I never wanted to be born into the royal family.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.46,0:07:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had been...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.97,0:07:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had been born as your son,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.30,0:07:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,everything would have been better.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.23,0:07:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.86,0:07:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy, Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.57,0:07:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go. I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.88,0:07:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There are some things that you only realize \Nonce you've experienced a loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.80,0:07:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You've noticed already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.30,0:07:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ragnar...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.22,0:07:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.43,0:07:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.35,0:07:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The time for you to awake has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.72,0:08:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No... Ragnar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.19,0:08:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.65,0:08:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.40,0:08:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish you well, Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.07,0:08:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ragnar...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be afraid! Attack together!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.40,0:08:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you hurt anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.57,0:08:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Those men are fighting over you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.41,0:09:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The winner is going to take you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.16,0:09:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a priest. Aren't you going \Nto stop them from fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.00,0:09:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a way to stop them? It's better \Nto let those who wish to die, die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.56,0:09:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.02,0:09:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a dream about Ragnar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.94,0:09:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He said goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.61,0:09:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a faithful man, even in death.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.20,0:09:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,In this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.99,0:09:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no one who loves me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.33,0:09:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You've found enlightenment. But you're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.80,0:09:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Was the emotion that Ragnar felt towards you love?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.51,0:10:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to keep you safe,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.18,0:10:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,he watched as 62 innocent villagers were killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.15,0:10:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.86,0:10:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Love...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.36,0:10:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.99,0:10:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know, these guys weren't that good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.82,0:10:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not easy to find strong opponents.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.37,0:10:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll never get to Valhalla.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.33,0:10:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the captain's duel still going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.42,0:10:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No way. He should have killed him instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.50,0:10:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what are they so excited about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.72,0:10:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go check.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.09,0:10:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.14,0:10:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.89,0:10:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.93,0:10:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.85,0:10:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.98,0:10:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.36,0:11:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.53,0:11:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,How could the captain...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.53,0:11:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He's getting beaten up by that kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.29,0:11:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice, Thorfinn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.75,0:11:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even have five men who'd be a match for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.13,0:11:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same chain mail as before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.84,0:11:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I should aim for tendons in his arms and legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.22,0:11:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to go after his vitals in London, \Nand I paid the price.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.18,0:11:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I can deliver the final blow once I stop him from moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.94,0:11:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I know you're strong, \Nbut your swordsmanship
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.94,0:11:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,is, well, only average.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.19,0:11:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There's still something missing \Nbefore you achieve perfection as a warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.95,0:11:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, then, \Nwhy are you having a hard time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.45,0:11:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.08,0:11:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm missing something, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.00,0:11:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought perhaps I could learn it from you, \Nsince you're Thors' child.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.71,0:12:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Thorfinn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.22,0:12:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.72,0:12:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it mean
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.60,0:12:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,to be a true warrior?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.86,0:12:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you asking what love is?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying that Ragnar didn't love me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.03,0:12:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.62,0:12:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let me ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.71,0:12:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If what Ragnar felt wasn't love,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.00,0:12:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,then who can embody love correctly?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.71,0:12:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.43,0:12:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.39,0:12:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,When he died, he became more beautiful \Nthan anyone among the living.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.56,0:12:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He's love itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.15,0:13:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll never hate others or steal anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.70,0:13:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He was abandoned there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.99,0:13:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going to give his body with generosity \Nto the beasts and the insects.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.04,0:13:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He lies exposed to the wind and the rain,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.25,0:13:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,but won't speak a single word in complaint.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.05,0:13:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Death...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.47,0:13:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,perfects a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.52,0:13:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.44,0:13:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.61,0:13:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.15,0:13:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.16,0:13:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it. \NI wasn't expecting you to know anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.58,0:13:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That was dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.21,0:14:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying that death is the essence of love?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.09,0:14:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.09,0:14:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what is the feeling when parents \Ncare for their children,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.30,0:14:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,when a husband and wife care for each other, \Nand when Ragnar cares about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.93,0:14:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's discrimination.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.40,0:14:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no different from fawning over a king \Nwhile hitting a slave with a whip.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.57,0:14:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,To Ragnar, you were more important \Nthan anyone else, Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.58,0:14:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably even more important than his own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.00,0:14:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,His tender feelings towards you were discrimination.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.93,0:14:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.47,0:14:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm beginning to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.31,0:15:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.27,0:15:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the fog has lifted.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.11,0:15:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.62,0:15:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.28,0:15:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He's done with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.87,0:15:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.88,0:15:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... It's still too shallow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.76,0:15:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm beginning to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.51,0:15:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This snow...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.64,0:15:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,is love, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.73,0:15:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.19,0:15:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.78,0:15:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.16,0:15:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.12,0:15:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The fog.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.08,0:15:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.37,0:16:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.63,0:16:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.96,0:16:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.01,0:16:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The creation of God is so beautiful. \NBut then why...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.06,0:16:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,is there no love...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.44,0:16:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,in the hearts of men?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.03,0:16:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,They say that the reason we turned into \Ncreatures like this
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.08,0:16:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,is because our ancestors disobeyed God
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.37,0:16:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and committed a sin long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.00,0:16:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We were...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.63,0:16:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,expelled from paradise.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.44,0:17:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.35,0:17:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.90,0:17:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.82,0:17:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He dampened the shock with his legs. Nice move.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.29,0:17:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.25,0:17:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.88,0:17:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He must be dead now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.09,0:17:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive, captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.88,0:17:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.18,0:17:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I've lost all hope now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.75,0:18:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like the battle is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.17,0:18:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.96,0:18:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,this is no good. That man has gone insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.01,0:18:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Highness. You had better run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.18,0:18:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sane?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.98,0:18:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Is anyone sane in this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.90,0:18:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.45,0:18:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.11,0:18:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No one knows how to love.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.29,0:18:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No one knows the meaning of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.33,0:18:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No one knows the meaning of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.08,0:18:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No one even knows the reason they're fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.21,0:18:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.80,0:19:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough. I'm sick of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.65,0:19:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What we lost in exchange for wisdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.62,0:19:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The most important thing... It's something
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.00,0:19:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,that we'll never get back as long as we live.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.17,0:19:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll never attain it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.63,0:19:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet, even then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.38,0:19:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You still tell us to seek it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.14,0:19:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Father in heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.82,0:19:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Miserable warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.99,0:20:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the farthest from love.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.07,0:20:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You, who have been expelled from paradise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.29,0:20:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't there any way to end the suffering \Nfrom your punishment other than death?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.84,0:20:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying that we only exist \Nso that we may be tested and endure?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.30,0:20:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Father in heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.26,0:20:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This man's soul cannot be saved \Nthrough the trials you set for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.63,0:20:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.67,0:20:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I no longer seek your salvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.84,0:21:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If you will no longer give us salvation,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.22,0:21:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,then, with our own hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.09,0:21:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,on this earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.05,0:21:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,we shall create our own paradise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.06,0:21:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.36,0:21:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.82,0:21:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince! Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.49,0:21:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, you fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.70,0:21:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't fight futile battles anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.00,0:21:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Futile?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.75,0:21:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wounds are deep. Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.00,0:21:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn. I slipped up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.88,0:21:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move. Your stomach is cut. Willibald!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.39,0:21:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Treat his wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.56,0:21:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to catch the horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.43,0:21:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You. Help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.14,0:22:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Highness, I've seen a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.52,0:22:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Be quiet and treat his wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.40,0:22:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Prince! Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.78,0:22:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to give you to Thorkell! \NOr else my buddies--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.12,0:22:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I was already planning to see Thorkell.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.50,0:22:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't be able to transport the wounded \Nunless we borrow their sleds.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.29,0:22:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You're talking nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.42,0:22:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea why I'm in \Nsuch a mess right now? You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.26,0:22:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If you get captured by Thorkell, \Nthen there will be no meaning to any of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.72,0:22:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Meaning?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.93,0:22:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say meaning?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.64,0:22:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The meaning of your battles?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.77,0:22:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no meaning to a battle like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.32,0:22:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So, don't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.65,0:22:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Warriors. Become my vassals.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.91,0:22:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall teach you about when you must fight, \Nand against whom.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.29,0:23:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall give meaning to your battles. \NTo your life and death.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.13,0:23:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.84,0:23:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the duty of a king is.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.52,0:00:25.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,見える
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.94,0:00:29.19,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,大丈夫だ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.28,0:00:38.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よく見てけばかわせる。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.99,0:00:42.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,当たらなきゃ…どんな武器もないのと同じだ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.30,0:00:50.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,シャッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.72,0:00:55.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いいぞコゾー！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.22,0:00:56.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,がんばれー！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.39,0:00:58.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やるのぅあのチビ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.47,0:01:00.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,大将に一撃入れたぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.72,0:01:02.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ああいうはしっこいのはしぶといぜ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.98,0:01:05.60,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,久々にいい勝負が見られるか！？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.65,0:01:10.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,クソ！斬れねェ…下に鎖かたびらを着てやがる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.57,0:01:12.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これ気に入ってたのに～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.94,0:01:17.62,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ウム！オレの斧を恐れないか。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.70,0:01:22.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,度胸はまずまず。そのへんはトールズゆずりだな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.41,0:01:27.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,デカブツてめぇ…父上のなんなんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.96,0:01:35.59,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前なんも聞いてないの？あいつも薄情だなァ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.67,0:01:38.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もとはヤルル…高貴な出だと聞いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.89,0:01:42.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ヤルルなのはヘルガの血筋だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.02,0:01:45.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,トールズは剣の腕で成り上がったのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.94,0:01:47.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なに…？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.19,0:01:49.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もっと聞きたい？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.77,0:01:51.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,聞きたい？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.28,0:01:56.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,聞きたかったらな。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.36,0:01:59.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もう少しオレを楽しませることだぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.95,0:02:01.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なァ！トルフィン
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.95,0:02:06.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,楽しませてやってもいいけどな。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.25,0:02:10.79,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,口が利ける程度に手加減すんのは難しいぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.34,0:02:16.38,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,言うねーコゾー！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.47,0:02:17.76,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ハラいてー！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.84,0:02:19.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,大将に手加減するとさあのチビ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.51,0:02:21.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お手柔らかにー！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.51,0:02:22.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,アホや！アホや！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.31,0:02:30.19,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おかしいか？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.27,0:02:33.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,トルフィンは俺の認めた戦士だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.36,0:02:34.53,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,笑うな！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.57,0:02:42.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,トールズはオレより強かった！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.99,0:02:46.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,自分がまさしくトールズの子だと証明してみせろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.04,0:02:48.33,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,トルフィン！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.93,0:04:33.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,バカガキめ…死にに戻ってきやがって…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.10,0:04:37.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,王子はどうなってやがる…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.66,0:04:50.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,近くで…戦の声がする…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.33,0:04:53.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ああ…もういいかげんにしてくれ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.71,0:04:57.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,他にすることはないのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.63,0:05:01.26,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,静かにしてくれ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.26,0:05:03.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,目を開けたくないんだ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.01,0:05:06.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,このまま寝ていたい…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.89,0:05:10.56,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,このまま…ずっと…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.02,0:05:17.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,殿下…殿下…クヌート殿下…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.83,0:05:33.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ラグナル…！お前、生きて…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.46,0:05:47.09,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これは…夢なのだな？ラグナル…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.14,0:05:52.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,はい。お別れを申し上げに参りました
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.14,0:06:00.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,逝くのか…僕を残して…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.61,0:06:08.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,僕ひとりで…こんな世界で生きてゆけというのか。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.78,0:06:11.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,生きてゆけると思うのか…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.50,0:06:19.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,私めは…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.96,0:06:25.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あなた様の教育係として失格でした
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.63,0:06:31.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あなた様をヤルルとしてではなく、ごく普通の…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.97,0:06:37.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それこそ農民が我が子を育てるがごとくにして参りました
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.52,0:06:44.65,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それが陛下のお望みではないと知りつつ…おゆるし下さい…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.61,0:06:54.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何がいけないのだ！\Nお前は父王陛下より僕自身の望みを汲んでくれた！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.83,0:07:04.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,王家になど…生まれたくなかった…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.46,0:07:08.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前の子に…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.97,0:07:14.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,僕はっ！お前の子に生まれていたら…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.30,0:07:17.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どんなに…よかったかと…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.23,0:07:22.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,殿下…！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.86,0:07:26.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,うれしゅうございます…殿下…！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.57,0:07:31.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いかないで…お前が好きなんだ…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.88,0:07:48.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,失って識ることがございます。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.80,0:07:52.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あなた様はすでにお気づきでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.30,0:07:53.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ラグナル…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.22,0:07:55.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,私めのことは夢でございます
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.43,0:07:56.26,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,待て…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.35,0:07:58.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もはや目覚める時が来たのです
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.72,0:08:01.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いやだ…ラグナル…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.19,0:08:02.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,戻れっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.65,0:08:04.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,戻れ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.40,0:08:10.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お健やかに。殿下…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.07,0:08:17.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ラグナル…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:38.56,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ビビるなァ！一斉にかかれ！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.40,0:08:49.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お体、痛みはございませんか？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.57,0:08:58.33,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの者たちは、殿下を得ようと争っているのです。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.41,0:09:01.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あなたは勝者のものになります
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.16,0:09:07.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,神父であろうそなた。争いを止めぬのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.00,0:09:14.55,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,止めようがありますか？死にたい者は死なせてやればよいのです
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.56,0:09:24.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,夢を見た。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.02,0:09:27.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ラグナルの夢だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.94,0:09:30.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,別れを告げられた。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.61,0:09:33.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,死んでまで律儀な男だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.20,0:09:39.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もうこの地上に…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.99,0:09:44.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,私を愛してくれる者はいなくなった
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.33,0:09:52.38,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それは大いなる悟りです。だが惜しい。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.80,0:09:58.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ラグナル殿のあなたへの思いは…愛ですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.51,0:10:02.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,彼はあなたの安全のために、
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.18,0:10:05.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,62人の善良な村人を見殺しにした
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.15,0:10:09.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,殿下。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.86,0:10:11.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,愛とは
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.36,0:10:12.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.99,0:10:19.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,しっかしよォ。手応えなかったなァこいつら
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.82,0:10:23.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,強ェ奴らにお目にかかるのは難しいよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.37,0:10:26.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いつまでたってもヴァルハラに行けやしねェ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.33,0:10:31.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まだ大将の決闘続いてんのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.42,0:10:33.42,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まさか。秒殺だろ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.50,0:10:35.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ならなんであんなに盛り上がってんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.72,0:10:39.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お…オレ見てくるわ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.09,0:10:40.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あぁオレも！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.14,0:10:41.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,オイオイどーなってんだよ！？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.89,0:10:44.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,殺っちめー！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.93,0:10:45.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,大将ー！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.85,0:10:46.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,てめェコゾー！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.98,0:10:48.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,逃げんなー！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.36,0:11:00.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,マジかよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.53,0:11:02.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの大将が…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.53,0:11:06.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やられっぱなしじゃねーか！あんな小僧に！！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.29,0:11:08.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いいぞトルフィン！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.75,0:11:13.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前にかなう奴ァオレの手下に5人といないだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.13,0:11:18.76,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,前と同じ鎖かたびらか…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.84,0:11:21.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,手足の腱を狙うのは有効だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.22,0:11:26.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ロンドンでは急所狙いで踏み込んで痛い目を見た。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.18,0:11:28.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,とどめはヤツの動きを止めてからだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.94,0:11:34.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だがなぁ…確かに強いが、お前の剣は…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.94,0:11:37.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんかこー…フツ～ってカンジ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.19,0:11:42.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,戦士として完成するには何かが足りない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.95,0:11:48.37,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ならそいつ相手にコテンパンのてめェはなんなんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.45,0:11:50.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうさ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.08,0:11:51.92,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,オレにも足りない。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.00,0:11:56.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,トールズの子のお前からならそれを学べると思ってたんだが…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.71,0:12:01.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なァ。トルフィンよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.22,0:12:02.72,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前はどう思う
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.72,0:12:08.60,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,本当の戦士って
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.60,0:12:10.56,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.86,0:12:21.65,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,愛とはなにか…だと？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:26.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ラグナルは私を愛していなかったというのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.03,0:12:28.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.62,0:12:32.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ならば問うのは私のほうだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.71,0:12:35.92,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ラグナルに愛がないのなら、
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.00,0:12:39.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,正しく愛を体現できる者はどこにいるのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.71,0:12:42.42,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そこに居ますよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.43,0:12:44.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ホラ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.39,0:12:55.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,彼は死んで、どんな生者よりも美しくなった。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.56,0:12:57.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,愛そのものといっていい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.15,0:13:05.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,彼はもはや、憎むことも奪うこともしません
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.70,0:13:09.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,彼はこのままここに打ち捨てられ、
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.99,0:13:14.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,その肉を獣や虫に惜しみなく与えるでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.04,0:13:19.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,雨風にさらされるがまま、
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.25,0:13:22.42,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それで一言半句の文句も言いません
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.05,0:13:26.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,死は…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.47,0:13:30.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,人間を完成させるのです
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.61,0:13:45.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,クソッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.15,0:13:47.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わからんか…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.16,0:13:50.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まァ気にすんなよ。そんなには期待してなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.58,0:13:53.37,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,姑息な手を！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.21,0:14:03.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,愛の本質が…死だというのか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.09,0:14:06.09,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.09,0:14:11.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ならば親が子を…夫婦が互いを、
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.30,0:14:15.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ラグナルが私を大切に思う気持ちは一体なんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.93,0:14:18.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,差別です。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.40,0:14:23.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,王にへつらい奴隷に鞭打つことと、たいして変わりません
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.57,0:14:30.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ラグナル殿にとって、王子殿下は他の誰よりも大切な人だったのです。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.58,0:14:34.79,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おそらく彼自身の命よりも…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.00,0:14:43.59,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,彼の…あなたに対する心弱い思いは…差別です
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.93,0:14:53.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうか…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.47,0:14:56.81,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わかってきた…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.31,0:15:02.19,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まるで…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.27,0:15:04.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,霧が晴れていくようだ…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.11,0:15:11.53,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あれ？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.62,0:15:13.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だーもーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.28,0:15:14.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,見切られてるぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.87,0:15:16.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ぬう…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.88,0:15:28.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,クソッ！まだ浅い！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.76,0:15:35.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わかってきた
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.51,0:15:36.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この雪が…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.64,0:15:40.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,愛、なのだな…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.73,0:15:43.19,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうです
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.19,0:15:48.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの空が…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.78,0:15:51.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの太陽が…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.16,0:15:54.03,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,吹きゆく風が…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.12,0:15:54.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,木々が…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.08,0:15:57.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,山々が…！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.37,0:16:03.38,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なのに…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.63,0:16:08.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんということだ…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.96,0:16:11.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,世界が…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.01,0:16:15.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,神の御技がこんなにも美しいというのに…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.06,0:16:20.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,人間の心には…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.44,0:16:23.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,愛がないのか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.03,0:16:35.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,私たちがこのような生き物になってしまったのは…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.08,0:16:40.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,遠い祖先が神に背き、
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.37,0:16:44.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,罪を犯したせいだといわれています
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.00,0:16:47.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,私たちは…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.63,0:16:51.55,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,楽園から追放されたのです
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.44,0:17:06.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あれ？おい！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.35,0:17:07.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どこ行った？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.90,0:17:10.73,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おい！アレって…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.82,0:17:15.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,足のバネで衝撃を殺したか！やるね！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.29,0:17:26.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あそこだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.25,0:17:27.79,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,すげー！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.88,0:17:29.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ありゃ死んだろー！？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.09,0:17:31.09,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さすが大将！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.88,0:17:34.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,クソ…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.18,0:17:37.59,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いよいよ万策尽きたか…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.75,0:18:07.79,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,決着がついたようですね。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.17,0:18:10.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だが…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.96,0:18:15.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いけませんな。あの者は正気を失っている
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.01,0:18:20.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,殿下。お逃げになったほうがよいでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.18,0:18:26.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,正気？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.98,0:18:31.73,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,正気の人間が、この世のどこにいるのだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.90,0:18:36.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,みな同じ…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.45,0:18:38.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,みな同じだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.11,0:18:44.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,誰もが等しく、愛することを知らぬのであろうが
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.29,0:18:47.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,生の意味を知らず、
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.33,0:18:49.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,死の意味を知らず、
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.08,0:18:52.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,己の戦う意味さえも知らぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.21,0:18:55.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.80,0:19:04.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もういい。もううんざりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.65,0:19:22.53,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,智を得て、かわりに失ったもの…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.62,0:19:26.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,最も大切なもの…そしてそれは
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.00,0:19:31.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,生ある限り、私たちの手には入らぬもの
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.17,0:19:37.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,手には入らぬ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.63,0:19:40.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それでも…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.38,0:19:42.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それでも追い求めよというのか！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.14,0:19:45.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,天の父よ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.82,0:19:59.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あわれな戦士。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.99,0:20:01.99,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,最も愛より遠き者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.07,0:20:04.99,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,楽園を追われし者よ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.29,0:20:18.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そなたたちの罰の苦しみは、死より他に終わらせるすべがないのか！？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.84,0:20:26.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,我々の生は！試され、耐え続けるためにのみあるというのか！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.30,0:20:28.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,天の父よ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.26,0:20:32.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あなたの与える試練では、この者の魂は救えぬ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.63,0:20:56.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,父よ…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.67,0:20:59.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もはやあなたの救いは求めぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.84,0:21:03.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あなたが与えてくれぬなら…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.22,0:21:05.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,我々の手で！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.09,0:21:06.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この地上に…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.05,0:21:08.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,再びの楽園を…！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.06,0:21:15.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あれ？王子？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.36,0:21:23.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いッてエェエエ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.82,0:21:25.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,王子！無事か！？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.49,0:21:29.62,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やめんか馬鹿者！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.70,0:21:31.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これ以上無益な争いをするな！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.00,0:21:33.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,むっ無益！？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.75,0:21:38.92,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,深手だな。大丈夫か？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.00,0:21:42.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,くそっ…ぬかったぜ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.88,0:21:46.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,動くな。腹をやられている。ヴィリヴァルド！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.39,0:21:50.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この者の手当てをしておけ。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.56,0:21:52.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,私は散った馬を捕まえる。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.43,0:21:54.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そなた、手伝え
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.14,0:22:00.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,殿下…私は…奇跡を見ました
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.52,0:22:02.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,黙って手当てにかかれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.40,0:22:06.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お、おい！ちょっ王子！どこ行く気だよ！？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.78,0:22:12.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あんたはトルケル軍に引き渡す！でないとオレの仲間が…！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.12,0:22:14.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もとよりトルケルの所へ行くつもりだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.50,0:22:19.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,連中にソリを借りねば、そのケガ人は運べぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.29,0:22:23.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なっ…！寝言ぬかすんじゃねーぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.42,0:22:27.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何のためにズタボロんなったと思ってんだボケ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.26,0:22:31.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,テメェがトルケルに捕まっちまったら…意味ねーんだよッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.72,0:22:33.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,意味？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.93,0:22:35.56,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,意味だと？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.64,0:22:37.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そなたたちの戦いのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.77,0:22:44.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こんな戦いに意味などない。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.32,0:22:46.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だからもう死ぬな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.65,0:22:51.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,戦士たちよ。私の家臣になれ。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.91,0:22:56.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,戦わねばならぬ時と相手を…教えてやろう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.29,0:23:02.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そなたたちの戦いに、生と死に。意味を与えてやろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.13,0:23:05.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それが…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.84,0:23:09.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,王の務めだ
